      <abstract>
        <p>Establishment of getto in Daugavpils (July 1941). Description of liquidation actions
          (1942). Mass executions during the final liquidation if the ghetto. Author’s life in
          German concentration camps in Toruń and Stutthof.</p>
      </abstract>
